{"id":258537,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/维权网-河北维权人士刘瑞生劳教上诉案将开庭（/","date":"2012-10-22T15:15:59Z","modified":"2012-10-22T15:15:59Z","title":"维权网 | 河北维权人士刘瑞生劳教上诉案将开庭（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\">  <br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<p>（维权网信息员蒋理报道）今天（10月22日），本网信息员获悉，河北省衡水市维权村民刘瑞生二次被劳教提起上诉案，已经定于本月25日（周四）在衡水市中级法院开庭。</p>\n<p>代理刘瑞生被劳教提起上诉案的北京莫少平律师事务所马纲权律师今天接到了河北衡水中级法院寄来的传票，告知本月25日在衡水中院29审判庭开庭。通知刚好是提前三天到律师手上。</p>\n<p>刘瑞生因为举报村中干部腐败、村财务不公开而遭到当地政府打压，先后被劳教二次，其中第一次劳教时他妻子也同时被劳教。</p>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-OIjfKb6zbmk/UIVOGDhH5oI/AAAAAAAARsY/5krjDikP87M/s1600/%E5%88%98%E7%91%9E%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%8A%E8%AF%89%E7%8A%B61.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-OIjfKb6zbmk/UIVOGDhH5oI/AAAAAAAARsY/5krjDikP87M/s320/%E5%88%98%E7%91%9E%E7%94%9F%E4%B8%8A%E8%AF%89%E7%8A%B61.JPG\" width=\"228\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-nBv9AYHgfgs/UIVF6uRoEXI/AAAAAAAARrg/_2gl2QYsOP8/s1600/%25E5%2588%2598%25E7%2591%259E%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25AF%2589%25E7%258A%25B62.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-nBv9AYHgfgs/UIVF6uRoEXI/AAAAAAAARrg/_2gl2QYsOP8/s320/%25E5%2588%2598%25E7%2591%259E%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25AF%2589%25E7%258A%25B62.jpg\" width=\"228\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-xtDHUQLVEFg/UIVOtZa_YWI/AAAAAAAARsg/kkxNDtmYHXA/s1600/%25E5%2588%2598%25E7%2591%259E%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25AF%2589%25E7%258A%25B63.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-xtDHUQLVEFg/UIVOtZa_YWI/AAAAAAAARsg/kkxNDtmYHXA/s320/%25E5%2588%2598%25E7%2591%259E%25E7%2594%259F%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25AF%2589%25E7%258A%25B63.JPG\" width=\"228\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Qu0bApOR54s/UIVPQHe23